description: This file defines a Java interface 'BrandingRepository' that extends JpaRepository to provide database operations related to 'Branding' entities, including a custom method to find branding records by partner.

classes.name: BrandingRepository
classes.description: A Spring Data JPA repository interface for the 'Branding' entity, providing CRUD operations and custom finder method.

methods.name: findByPartner
methods.description: Custom method to retrieve a list of 'Branding' entities associated with a given 'Partner'.
